data.description: *Open Houses Feb 5th 10-2 and Feb 8th 4-6.   BEAUTIFUL AND BRAND NEW! This stylish landscaped all brick home has fabulous features! The high trey ceilings, open floor plan, upgraded lighting and plumbing fixtures, and upgraded base boards and casings throughout the home, all create a sense of style hard to find in new construction. The large foyer, living room, kitchen, dining area and utility room have luxurious vinyl plank flooring. The bedrooms are furnished with upgraded carpeting and large closets. The kitchen is designed with stainless steel appliances including a refrigerator, large pantry, high quality custom cabinets with soft close doors and drawers, a large island with additional cabinet storage, and upgraded granite counter tops. The roomy utility room has convenient cabinets for storage and granite countertops. There is a convenient half bath located off of the great room. The tiled master bath has a double vanity, granite counter tops, a large tiled shower, soaking tub and two walk in closets. The two additional bedrooms are connected by a full bathroom with separate toilets, sinks and large walk in closets. Ceiling fans are in each bedroom, great room and covered patio. Additional upgrades include a sprinkler system with well pump, privacy fence and gates, covered porch and garage door opener. This house has been built with amazing quality and impeccable style! It's time to make it your new home!
